{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was all stupid-- it didn't make sense because the girl behind the typewriter didn't paying any attention to it, didn't listen to it, no matter what you said.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You could have said, I just came from the Mars, and I landed here, OK?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It would have been OK, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you knew it didn't make any sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was because so they had a better job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that took forever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you were outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know that, when we first lined up, there was a man who said, the commander is coming.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And first, you had two of the German Shepherds racing through, which scared the daylights out of you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then came the commander.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he went along the line and said, Jew, Jew, Jew, Jew, Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he came to me, I said no, I'm Mischling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after he passed, I remember I had an envelope to give him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it scared me, but I thought, if I don't give it to him, who knows what's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at the end of the row, I said, Herr Kommandant, excuse me, I need to give you something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my heart was going like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took the envelope from me-- he never opened it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He handed it to the next guy and went on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the moment I said no, I'm not Jew, I'm-- I'm Mischling, they hung a sign around me with a big E.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "E4-- E means in German, what it meant is entscheidung-- decision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The decision has not been made yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the others got a number-- number such and such.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I learned really quickly that E was much better than a number, because number meant eventually transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
